A '''Guild Master''',<ref name="Chapter 21" /> also known as a '''Guild Boss''',<ref name="Handbook">''[[Star Wars: The Mandalorian Handbook]]''</ref> was a position held by the leader of a guild. During the [[New Republic Era]], [[Greef Karga]] served as the Guild Master of the [[Nevarro Hunters]].<ref name="Chapter 21" />

